entries.s_fc01f22f: Those Black Sun fighters are history.
entries.s_f3a2a7d2: I can't believe you aborted the first mission I gave you! I hope you're here to try again, soldier!
entries.s_ef7c4c8: Do you have a progress report for me, pilot?
entries.s_e3034e87: Look for any Black Sun craft in the area. They'll likely bring skiffs, some fighters, and maybe even a handful of gunboats.
entries.s_ce77bdfc: Hmm. This seems a bit rough.
entries.s_c49dadaf: Sweep is done, and our ship is safe.
entries.s_c1cb6e44: If you weren't ready, you should've said so!
entries.s_bf46ea6c: Deep in Tatooine system quadrant III. I think they're prepping to stage an assault on the Hutts... and a lot of our friends could get caught in the cross-fire.
entries.s_b76bbf5f: Good. One of our top pilots is using a modified Y-Wing in this system to gather sensor data for the Alliance. Meet him at the rally point, and make sure he finishes his sensor sweep in one piece!
entries.s_b65b63e: Outstanding! Let me know when you are ready to fly again!
entries.s_b2f0eabb: C'mon, I'm just kidding. What say you fly for me? Bust up a Black Sun fighter rally in Quad III?
entries.s_add38b4: Are you kidding me? This is the Alliance, friend! Straighten up!
entries.s_adb01382: The Black Sun are moving in to challenge the Hutts for this bit of the Outer Rim. That means bloodshed, and that's bad news for us!
entries.s_ad45bcbf: Talk to the general. She'll have work for you.
entries.s_9d805e09: They want to cut a hole through the Outer Rim to run spice, and they're sick of trying to negotiate with the Hutts...
entries.s_9ccfeefa: Outstanding! Talk to me when you're ready to fly again.
entries.s_95ca3dcc: Perfect. We have word that a Black Sun assassin force is gathering strength somewhere deep in the Tatooine system.
entries.s_8af71059: So. I hear it was pretty rough out there. Would you like to try helping us again?
entries.s_803bce3f: Gonzo dangerous! An INSANE mission that will kill you flat out!
entries.s_7f5b6f74: Good! Eliminate all Black Sun fighters at this nav point and return to me when you are finished.
entries.s_7aa2ae19: Heh. Get some missions under your belt, friend. Then come talk to me.
entries.s_56ea3421: You'll know when you need to know. Talk to the general. She's bound to have work for you.
entries.s_4e1e1511: Seems like a waste of resources.
entries.s_49580a34: You know, that would take a long time to explain. Look - I need someone with guts to take flight against a swarm of assassins. Are you interested?
entries.s_4021e802: What sort of ships should I target?
entries.s_3e8d2533: Are you ready for a very dangerous mission?
entries.s_340e3cc: How did the sensor sweep go?
entries.s_32c77056: I have nothing to say to you.
entries.s_32761c80: Excellent! The Force be with you, friend! See you soon.
entries.s_32583e8e: No, I haven't even left yet.
entries.s_24fcd0f1: Well, if you're not ready - just say so!
entries.s_1d2c155d: Hold on, pal. I don't think you're ready to work for me, yet.
entries.s_14bb212a: Then get back out there and make it happen!
entries.s_113f133e: Are you ready for your next assignment?
